text:
So, perhaps Craigslist isn't the typical place to look for a "gentleman" but I decided to give it a shot nonetheless. What I am really looking for is a man who is self-assured and understands what he wants. It would also be nice to go out with someone who is willing to take things slow. I don't have a list of criteria that I expect my ideal date to fulfill. However, it would be appreciated if one is intelligent enough to construct a sentence. I prefer quiet and laid back settings where conversation has the opportunity to flourish.

Please only message me if you have serious intentions. I am not looking for a one night hookup. I am not impressed by what you may claim to be your yearly income so do not bother telling me in your first message because it will result in an immediate delete. Just be interesting and genuine!

On a final note, it helps if you appreciate people who may be a tad unusual ;}
